parameters:
"I was pulled away by someone... Did I get separated from
Onee-san...?"\n<Saku>\FF[23]

(...This shape... Is it a key? If I give it to Onee-san,
she'll surely be delighted.)\F[22]
(...It doesn't seem like she's wearing anything)
"Hii, no... don't touch me, stop it... mmmph!"\n<Saku>\FF[27]

The tentacle, reminiscent of a serpent of flesh, wraps
around Saku's body and pierces something into her neck.
\FF[27]\AA[N]
"Ouch! What is this cold thing entering...?"\n<Saku>\FF[21]

At that moment, Saku's consciousness rapidly fades away.
\FF[21]\AA[N]
"My body suddenly feels... so heavy, ugh..."\n<Saku>\FF[23]
